Package: airportr
Type: Package
Title: Convenience tools for working with airport data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dmitry Shkolnik
Maintainer: The package maintainer <shkolnikd@gmail.com>
Description: This package takes open source airport data and provides tools to look up information, translate names into codes and vice-verse, as well as some basic calculation functions for measuring distances.
License: The data is under an Open Database License and code is under an MIT license. 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr
